4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive AI Machine Learning Engineer bootcamp designed for beginners with no prior knowledge. The course spans 16 weeks, featuring three classes per week in small groups of up to 12 students. Students will learn Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and various statistical techniques, developing skills to create predictive models and work with both supervised and unsupervised learning algorithms. Participants will tackle real-world scenarios and gain practical experience in deploying AI projects. The certification earned is recognized by multiple organizations. Classes are available in English and Spanish. For more information, visit: [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop